for the fun five minutes.

04:51.031 --> 04:52.065
Ten minutes.

04:52.066 --> 04:53.232
Ten is good, right?

05:00.508 --> 05:02.075
Konichiwa, dude.

05:02.076 --> 05:04.810
Release the lizards!

05:06.313 --> 05:08.348
I don't get your show, Murph.

05:08.349 --> 05:09.482
Yeah!

05:09.483 --> 05:12.018
Why are some of the Tokyo
Fun Time Lizards real

05:12.019 --> 05:14.955
and some are women in lizard suits?

05:14.956 --> 05:16.623
You know, man, after the second day,

05:16.624 --> 05:19.558
I just stopped asking questions.

05:20.327 --> 05:21.928
Great work, team.

05:21.929 --> 05:24.631
And the necklaces look fantastic.

05:24.632 --> 05:27.500
Oh, but remember, it's two
hex cuts between every rondelle

05:27.501 --> 05:29.402
and every third
cloisonnÃ© should be onyx.

05:29.403 --> 05:31.705
I tried to tell them
that, but I couldn't

05:31.706 --> 05:33.673
say any of those words.

05:33.674 --> 05:36.710
Well, maybe this is distracting you.

05:36.711 --> 05:38.044
What is this?

05:38.045 --> 05:40.013
Some kind of reptile porn?

05:41.148 --> 05:43.249
No, that's just my game show.

05:43.250 --> 05:45.984
Though I did have sex with
that lizard woman on the left.

05:47.287 --> 05:49.489
But, serious, you guys,

05:49.490 --> 05:51.825
I just wanted to say
thank you so, so much.

05:51.826 --> 05:54.728
