future in your hands.

05:54.729 --> 05:57.897
Your greasy, greasy, hands.

05:57.898 --> 05:59.866
Yeah, look!

05:59.867 --> 06:02.369
I made a necklace completely
out of onion rings.

06:02.370 --> 06:04.904
Maybe we could take a break

06:04.905 --> 06:07.206
on the ol' onion rings.

06:08.274 --> 06:10.744
Who wants to help me
pick out pocket squares?

06:10.745 --> 06:12.008
OSCAR, TEDDY and MURPH: Not it!

06:12.009 --> 06:13.913
Not... damn it!

06:13.914 --> 06:16.349
Well, I've noticed
that Charlotte prefers

06:16.350 --> 06:18.485
solid colors over
patterns, so I can't decide

06:18.486 --> 06:19.749
whether to go with the white...

06:19.750 --> 06:22.288
or the more daring cream.

06:22.289 --> 06:24.324
I don't know, why not the cream?

06:24.325 --> 06:26.292
Why not indeed!

06:27.361 --> 06:29.896
I will be the re-bel of the ball.

06:29.897 --> 06:30.997
And she will be

06:30.998 --> 06:32.932
