I'm surprised you're up so early.

08:54.530 --> 08:55.993
You were out so late with Charlotte.

08:55.994 --> 08:57.131
What? No, we weren't!

08:57.132 --> 08:59.232
Out for... normal amount of time.

08:59.634 --> 09:00.902
Morning.

09:00.903 --> 09:02.303
Hey, babe.

09:02.304 --> 09:03.204
Speaking of normal.

09:03.205 --> 09:04.272
There's normal Charlotte.

09:04.273 --> 09:06.641
My normal friend.

09:06.642 --> 09:09.043
Felix, I had so much fun last night.

09:09.044 --> 09:10.645
Normal amount of fun.

09:10.646 --> 09:12.347
And guess what.

09:12.348 --> 09:13.982
Bryn Terfel is in town tonight

09:13.983 --> 09:16.985
singing Scarpia in Tosca.

09:16.986 --> 09:19.921
Now you're just saying things.

09:19.922 --> 09:22.957
And I got us two tickets!

09:22.958 --> 09:24.259
Oh, tonight?

09:24.260 --> 09:25.260
I don't... I don't...

09:25.261 --> 09:26.361
Not you, Oscar.

09:26.362 --> 09:27.728
For me and Felix.

09:28.596 --> 09:29.530
Oh.

09:29.531 --> 09:31.165
Of course.

09:31.166 --> 09:33.368
Tosca is one of your favorites, right?

09:33.369 --> 09:35.169
Of course.

09:35.170 --> 09:39.474
But I feel like I have been
monopolizing your time, so...

09:39.475 --> 09:41.142
Not at all.

09:41.143 --> 09:43.311
"Please," she asked,

09:43.312 --> 09:45.713
having just bought two
very expensive tickets?

09:45.714 --> 09:48.783
Well...

09:48.784 --> 09:50.784
Great, it's a date!

09:51.419 --> 09:53.254
Not a date!

09:53.255 --> 09:55.222
But I will attend next to you.

09:59.394 --> 10:01.695
Not plugged in there, pal.

10:02.563 --> 10:04.264
Just practicing.

10:08.336 --> 10:09.737
Only 28?

10:09.738 --> 10:10.801
We are falling way behind,

10:10.802 --> 10:11.706
people!

10:11.707 --> 10:13.908
We're just so hungry.

10:13.909 --> 10:15.910
I can go pick up some burgers.

10:15.911 --> 10:18.413
The only thing I need you
picking up is the pace.

10:18.414 --> 10:20.315
My deadline is tomorrow.

10:20.316 --> 10:22.649
You can eat then.

10:24.485 --> 10:26.187
This is not fun anymore.

10:26.188 --> 10:28.990
She wouldn't let me go to the bathroom.

10:28.991 --> 10:30.024
Hey, shh!

10:30.025 --> 10:31.359
She'll hear us talking.

10:31.360 --> 10:33.361
No one make any noise!

10:33.362 --> 10:35.429
Get that phone, man!

10:43.504 --> 10:44.772
It's from Charlotte.

10:44.773 --> 10:46.074
She's at the opera.

10:46.075 --> 10:47.709
She says they're about to have

10:47.710 --> 10:49.176
a night they'll never forget.

10:51.012 --> 10:53.681
Hey, it isn't weird that
Charlotte likes to go out

10:53.682 --> 10:55.149
with Felix all the time, is it?

10:55.150 --> 10:56.084
No, it is.

10:56.085 --> 10:57.285
Definitely weird.

10:57.286 --> 10:58.553
Can you blame her?

10:58.554 --> 11:00.421
I'd be bummed if my
boyfriend didn't want to do

11:00.422 --> 11:01.689
the things I love.

11:01.690 --> 11:03.925
Not a good sign if you're
in it for the long haul.

11:03.926 --> 11:05.960
But I am in it for the long haul.

11:05.961 --> 11:07.664
- Doesn't seem like it.
- Sure don't.

11:07.665 --> 11:10.631
You know, part of being
in a long-term relationship

11:10.632 --> 11:12.232
is acting like you love stuff you don't.

11:12.256 --> 11:14.869
Like, "Sure, baby, I'd
love to spend Saturday

11:14.870 --> 11:16.236
in the Wig District."

11:19.640 --> 11:21.576
Where are you going?

11:21.577 --> 11:23.677
To the opera-singing place!

11:27.048 --> 11:28.416
Where's Oscar?

11:28.417 --> 11:31.085
Did he take an
unauthorized bathroom break?

11:31.086 --> 11:33.121
He's at the opera.

11:33.122 --> 11:35.590
Hilarious, Teddy.

11:35.591 --> 11:38.259
I guess we will all have
to work that much harder.

11:38.260 --> 11:39.694
You know what?

11:39.695 --> 11:41.061
If Oscar's out, I'm out.

11:41.889 --> 11:42.930
This is worse than hosting

11:42.931 --> 11:44.065
that Japanese game show.

11:44.066 --> 11:47.268
And they put jumper
cables on my nipples.

11:47.269 --> 11:48.569
I'm out too.

11:48.570 --> 11:49.736
You're mean.

11:50.838 --> 11:52.807
