this by ourselves, right?

11:59.581 --> 12:02.383
We will work here all night

12:02.384 --> 12:04.185
if we have to.

12:04.186 --> 12:05.886
Right?

12:11.259 --> 12:13.027
I didn't get a program.

12:13.028 --> 12:14.395
Can I look over your shoulder?

12:16.465 --> 12:20.401
Oh, you have an eyelash on your cheek.

12:20.402 --> 12:23.204
Leave it, just leave it.

12:23.205 --> 12:24.972
Hey, opera buddies.

12:24.973 --> 12:26.474
Oscar!

12:26.475 --> 12:27.498
What are you doing here?!

12:27.499 --> 12:28.409
Well, I had to see

12:28.410 --> 12:29.744
what the opera was all about.

12:29.745 --> 12:31.279
Can't let you two have all the fun.

12:31.280 --> 12:32.547
And to class up the night,

12:32.548 --> 12:33.948
I brought this.

12:33.949 --> 12:35.716
Chips.

12:35.717 --> 12:36.984
In a tube.

12:36.985 --> 12:40.455
Oscar, I know you hate
all this cultural stuff.

12:40.456 --> 12:41.756
You don't have to be here.

12:41.757 --> 12:42.690
But I want to be here.

12:42.691 --> 12:44.358
What you like, I like.

12:44.359 --> 12:46.127
Your thing is my thing.

12:46.128 --> 12:49.297
It's Tosca...

12:49.298 --> 12:50.597
I'm Osca.

12:51.933 --> 12:54.035
That's sweet.

12:54.036 --> 12:55.770
But I think when it comes to opera,

12:55.771 --> 12:57.071
you either like it or you don't.

12:57.072 --> 12:58.539
Right, Felix?

12:58.540 --> 13:01.342
Wouldn't you describe it
as a feeling in your soul?

13:04.346 --> 13:06.226
Oh, thank God, it's starting.

13:06.250 --> 13:07.381
What's this one about?

13:07.382 --> 13:10.818
Tosca is a tragic love triangle.

13:10.819 --> 13:12.720
Is there any other kind?

13:12.721 --> 13:17.291
It's about a happy couple
and an evil man named Scarpia

13:17.292 --> 13:20.060
intent on stealing the woman away.

13:21.729 --> 13:25.032
He's a bad, bad, evil man.

13:25.033 --> 13:27.067
Does he get away with it?

13:28.069 --> 13:29.402
No! He doesn't!

13:30.667 --> 13:31.707
I've fallen for Charlotte!

13:31.708 --> 13:33.665
I didn't mean for it
to happen, it just did!

13:34.709 --> 13:37.043
Don't look at me! I'm a monster!

13:45.942 --> 13:47.943
Felix? Felix?

13:49.174 --> 13:51.608
His vacuum cleaner is here.

13:52.576 --> 13:54.411
